	</div></div></div></div></div><div class="content-wrapper"><div class="main-content max-width min-width center"><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-12"><div class="layout-cell-pad-main"><img class="foto" src="http://servicosweb.cnpq.br/wspessoa/servletrecuperafoto?tipo=1&amp;id=K4849078H7"><div class="infpessoa"><h2 class="nome" tabindex="0">Renner Sartório Camargo</h2><ul class="informacoes-autor"><li><span class="img_link icone-informacao-autor"></span>Endereço para acessar este CV: http://lattes.cnpq.br/3539297708118726</li><li><span class="img_identy icone-informacao-autor"></span>ID Lattes: <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #326C99;">3539297708118726</span></li><li><span class="img_cert icone-informacao-autor"></span>Última atualização do currículo em 31/10/2025</li></ul></div><br class="clear"><div class="title-wrapper"><h1 class="ui-hidden" tabindex="0"></h1><hr class="separator"><p class="resumo">I hold a Ph.D. in Electrical Engineering from the Federal University of Espírito Santo (Ufes), with a doctoral research period (sandwich program) conducted in conjunction with the University of Alcalá de Henares (UAH), Madrid, Spain, in the laboratory of the GEISER group (Electronic Engineering Applied to Renewable Energy Systems). I also hold Master's (MSc) and Bachelor's (BSc) degrees in Electrical Engineering (Ufes) and an MBA in Industrial Project Engineering.Currently, I am the Coordinator of the Control and Automation Engineering Course at the Federal Institute of Espírito Santo (Ifes) - Serra Campus (since 2022) and Coordinator of the Postgraduate Program in Renewable Energy (Ifes/UnAC). I am a permanent faculty member of the Postgraduate Program in Control and Automation Engineering (ProPECAut) - Professional Master's in Control and Automation Engineering at Ifes Campus Serra.In the research field, I am a member of the Research Group on Renewable Energy for Automation (GERA) and develop activities at the Microgrids and Renewable Energy Laboratory (LaMER). During my doctorate (Ufes/UAH), I researched multilevel converters and electrical drives based on predictive control and PWM implementations in FPGA and DSP.I have nearly ten years of experience in developing building projects, electrical installations, substations, and lightning protection systems. I participated in the creation of a socio-environmental committee with an emphasis on energy efficiency, power quality improvement, and raising awareness for the sustainable use of resources.Areas of expertise: smart grids and microgrids, electric mobility, electric machine drives, embedded systems, and artificial intelligence.<span class="texto" style="font-weight: bold"> (Texto informado pelo autor)</span></p></div><br class="clear"><div class="title-wrapper"><a name="Identificacao" tabindex="39"><h1 tabindex="0">Identificação</h1></a><hr class="separator"><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-12 data-cell"><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right"><div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right"><b>Nome</b></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9"><div class="layout-cell-pad-5">Renner Sartório Camargo<img src="/buscatextual/images/icon-rfb.png" class="alinhamento-texto-img" title="Dados cadastrais validados junto a Receita Federal do Brasil"></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right"><div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right"><b>Nome em citações bibliográficas</b></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9"><div class="layout-cell-pad-5">CAMARGO, R. S.;Sartório Camargo, Renner;SARTORIO CAMARGO, RENNER;Camargo, Renner Sartorio;Camargo, Renner Sartório;Camargo, Renner S.;Renner Sartório Camargo;Renner Sartorio Camargo;CAMARGO, R.S.</div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right"><div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right"><b>Lattes iD</b></div></div><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9"><div class="layout-cell-pad-5"><img src="./images/v2/icone_lattes.png" style="width: 15px; margin-righ